/span>建人出來」</strong></span>"},{"pid":"daca7ee414b7c9aa397ad0a64bc91d30b685fd8d","tid":2123471,"uid":310688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2337ed4a6913a02f0774e30f789f6ff5205473c0","tid":2123471,"uid":134247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8de651eb408f6b3cd3a16a13cd57a917200d2bbf","tid":2123471,"uid":236404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"987562db530b105f71fe3578c74e9d4e10762229","tid":2123471,"uid":134247,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T17:22:45.000Z","msg":"台語當然真趣味，趕緊來學<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算識廣東話，學台語有啲位都好kick<br />\n台語本身個文讀白讀系統係勁之煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如 人=lang; 人生=jin sin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T17:54:55.000Z","msg":"閩語文白二讀嘅情況，等於日本語嘅訓讀與音讀<br />\n例如   赤<br />\n訓讀 係 aka<br />\n音讀 係 seki <br />\n<br />\n韓語、越南語、壯語好多字都係咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T00:25:13.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廣東話、客家話都無台語咁癲<br />\n有啲熟語係兩個音齊齊用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T08:21:13.000Z","msg":"閩語係脫胎自上古同中古漢語<br />\n讀音句法早就自成一格 所以福建嘅語言喺唐宋就已經同中原唔同 唐宋以後嘅讀書人為咗去學中原音韻 就模仿當時官話標準讀音發明出文讀 去區別日常生活講嘢嘅白讀音 所以變咗日常交流同讀詩詞/文章會用兩套截然不同嘅讀音 由於閩南地理位置比其他閩語封閉 所以可以同時保留文白二讀兩套系統<br />\n<br />\n至於粵客基本上係同源 係由中古漢語演變出嚟 所以冇必要發明一套新系統嘅文讀方法 所以訓讀同白讀相差唔大"},{"pid":"79cd1a67a21e57de5671c80a0094826b96f390e9","tid":2123471,"uid":134247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"daca7ee414b7c9aa397ad0a64bc91d30b685fd8d","tid":2123471,"uid":310688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2337ed4a6913a02f0774e30f789f6ff5205473c0","tid":2123471,"uid":134247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8de651eb408f6b3cd3a16a13cd57a917200d2bbf","tid":2123471,"uid":2